            [start_date] => 27/06/2024 10:45 AM
            [end_date]   => 01/07/2024 10:45 AM
        )
)
```

---

**Note:**  
- This assumes each process starts exactly at the previous process's end time.
- Adjust according to holidays or workdays if needed using [Carbon's business day packages](https://github.com/kylekatarnls/business-day).
