## **7. Going Further**

- **Full rigid body resolution:** Consider angular velocity, moment of inertia, and more.
- **Advanced response:** Implement constraints, stacking, static/dynamic/kinematic types.
- **Performance:** Use broadphase (sweep and prune), and only resolve necessary pairs.

